ongly suggesting that it must have been heated during\nprevious dynamical encounters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Dec 2008 22:38:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2009 20:23:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
